# 2. Project Scope

## 2.1 In Scope (MVP)

### Authentication & Roles

- JWT-based authentication (HttpOnly cookies)
- Role-based access:
  - Admin
  - Staff
  - Patron

### Catalog Management

- Book metadata storage
- Multiple physical copies per book (`BookCopy`)
- Search and filtering
- Dewey Decimal categorization

### AI-Assisted Book Ingestion

- Image upload (cover or spine)
- OCR text extraction (AWS Textract)
- ISBN detection
- Metadata enrichment (OpenAI GPT)
- Dewey classification suggestions
- Manual review and override before saving

### Circulation System

- Book check-in / check-out
- Due dates
- Overdue tracking
- Basic fine calculation
- Copy location tracking and shelving

### Library Map System

- Custom 2D map with labeled shelf sections
- Clickable shelf zones
- Zoom-in first-person shelf view
- Zoom-out to full map

### AI Organizational Recommendations

Generated suggestions based on:

- Dewey classification
- Shelf capacity
- Current placement

Recommendations are advisory only.

---

## 2.2 Out of Scope (MVP)

The following are stretch features and will not be implemented in the initial release:

- Drag-and-drop shelf reorganization
- Duplicate / missing-volume detection
- Analytics dashboard
- Barcode / QR generation
- Multilingual UI support
- User-defined tags or collections
- Custom map editor

