# 5. System Architecture

ShelfSight follows a three-layer architecture:

## Frontend Layer

- Next.js 16 web interface (App Router)
- Catalog UI
- Circulation interface
- Interactive 2D library map (React Flow)
- Ingestion review interface
- Reports dashboard

## Backend Layer

- Node.js + Express REST API
- Prisma ORM
- PostgreSQL 16 database
- JWT authentication (HttpOnly cookies) and RBAC

## AI / Data Processing Layer

- OCR extraction (AWS Textract)
- ISBN detection
- Metadata enrichment (OpenAI GPT)
- Dewey classification suggestions

AI outputs are reviewed by librarians before being committed to the catalog.

