# 13. Agent Guardrails and Instructions

## 13.1 Phase Gates

### Phases 1–4 (Foundation)

Must be completed before UI work begins:

- Repo setup
- API contract
- Authentication system
- CRUD APIs

### Phases 5–7 (Core UI + Integration)

Do NOT connect frontend to backend until:

- Endpoints return correct responses
- curl/Postman verification passes

### Phases 8–10 (Map + AI)

Map and OCR systems depend on:

- Completed catalog features
- Connected circulation workflows

### Phases 11–13 (Polish + Deploy)

Deployment requires:

- All MVP functionality operational
- Alpha milestone fully tested

